==English==

===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# Not [[inside]] a house or under covered structure; unprotected; in the [[open]] air.
#:''They went '''outdoors''' to light up their cigarettes.''

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{context|often preceded by "the"}} The [[environment]] outside of [[enclosed]] [[structure]]s; the [[natural]] environment in the open air.
#:''She loves the '''outdoors'''.''

